Project Description
JC is a Windows tray application controlling Jenkins factory. Among others, you can view, run, stop jobs, view build output and download generated artifacts.



Jenkins Controller use Jenkins .NET Client NuGet package: https://jenkinscontroller.codeplex.com/wikipage?title=Jenkins%20.NET%20Client%20%28NuGet%20package%29
